WEBVTT

00:01.355 --> 00:05.069
Ergonomically designed to fit within the palm of your hand,...

00:05.425 --> 00:08.497
...Fold's compact outer display is the first...

00:08.669 --> 00:12.478
...to enable truly one-handed, on-the-go responses.

00:13.830 --> 00:18.138
Fold's app continuity seamlessly configures your favorite apps...

00:19.127 --> 00:21.700
...while the software optimization with Google...

00:22.020 --> 00:25.761
...allows you, for the first time on mobile, to watch a video on Youtube,...

00:26.609 --> 00:32.224
...text your friend about it and book your stay, all at the same time.

00:33.417 --> 00:36.329
When it comes to capturing your own content,...

00:36.806 --> 00:41.402
...Fold's prograde, six-camera system makes every angle epic,...

00:42.343 --> 00:46.795
...from everyday spontaneous moments to the triple rear system,...

00:47.393 --> 00:52.729
...to capturing unsurpassed 123 degrees ultrawide shots.

00:54.851 --> 00:57.964
Available as both a 4G and 5G model,...

00:58.269 --> 01:01.879
...its unparalleled, high-speed performance comes from not one...

01:02.181 --> 01:07.194
...but two batteries, which combine to form a single revolutionary energy cell,...

01:08.617 --> 01:11.883
...giving you the power to share power on even on the go.

